<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="151" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="151">
<taxonomicName LSID="29598963-BCC5-524E-AB34-094F8FA0A166" authority="(Geoffroy, 1785)" authorityName="Panzer" authorityYear="1801" baseAuthorityName="Geoffroy" baseAuthorityYear="1785" class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Dolerus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Dolerus bimaculatus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bimaculatus">Dolerus bimaculatus (Geoffroy, 1785)</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="151" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="151">
<taxonomicName authorityName="Geoffroy" authorityYear="1785" class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Tenthredo" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tenthredo bimaculata" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bimaculata">Tenthredo bimaculata</taxonomicName>
Geoffroy in Fourcroy, 1785: 368, not 386 as given by 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.2580.1.1" author="Taeger, A" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" pagination="1 - 1064" refId="B173" refString="Taeger, A, Blank, SM, Liston, AD, 2010. World Catalog of Symphyta (Hymenoptera). Zootaxa 2580 (1): 1 - 1064, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.2580.1.1" title="World Catalog of Symphyta (Hymenoptera)." url="https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.2580.1.1" volume="2580" year="2010">Taeger et al. (2010)</bibRefCitation>
. Sex not given. Syntypes (assumed). Type locality: France. The earlier description in French by 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.154767" author="Geoffroy, EL" journalOrPublisher="Kongliga Vetenskaps Academiens nya Handlingar" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" refId="B51" refString="Geoffroy, EL, 1762. Histoire abregee des Insectes qui se trouvent aux environs de Paris; Dans laquelle ces Animaux sont ranges suivant un ordre methodique. Durand, Paris, 2: 690 pp. [+plates 11-22.] https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.154767" title="Histoire abregee des Insectes qui se trouvent aux environs de Paris; Dans laquelle ces Animaux sont ranges suivant un ordre methodique. Durand, Paris, 2: 690 pp. [+ plates 11 - 22.]" url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.154767" year="1762">Geoffroy (1762</bibRefCitation>
: 279, no. 16).
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="151">
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Tenthredo" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tenthredo tristis" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tristis">Tenthredo tristis</taxonomicName>
Fabricius, 1804: 39. Sex not given. Syntypes (assumed). Type locality: Germany (&quot;Habitat in Germania Dr. Panzer.&quot;). Lectotype designated below. Primary homonym of 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Tenthredo" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tenthredo tristis" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tristis">Tenthredo tristis</taxonomicName>
Fabricius, 1779.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="151" type="type material">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Type material examined and taxonomic notes.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="151">
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Tenthredo" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tenthredo tristis" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tristis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Tenthredo tristis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Fabricius, 1804. Lectotype ♂ hereby designated, labelled: &quot; 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Tenthredo" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tenthredo tristis" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tristis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Tenthredo tristis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
&quot;, &quot;LECTOTYPE 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Tenthredo" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tenthredo tristis" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tristis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Tenthredo tristis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Fabricius, 1775 [sic!] des. SMBlank 2008&quot; [red, printed], &quot; 
<taxonomicName authority="Panzer, 1801" authorityName="Panzer" authorityYear="1801" baseAuthorityName="Geoffroy" baseAuthorityYear="1785" class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Dolerus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Dolerus bimaculatus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bimaculatus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Dolerus bimaculatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Geoff.) [handwritten] det. S.M.Blank 2008 ✓&quot; [printed], &quot; 
<taxonomicName authority="Panzer, 1801" authorityName="Panzer" authorityYear="1801" baseAuthorityName="Geoffroy" baseAuthorityYear="1785" class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Dolerus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Dolerus bimaculatus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bimaculatus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Dolerus bimaculatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Geoffroy) M.Heidemaa det.&quot; [printed], &quot; ZMUC-GISHym 1067&quot;. Left flagellum, right flagellomeres 6-7, left fore tarsomeres 4-5 missing. ZMUC.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="151">
Contrary to 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Fabricius’">Fabricius'</normalizedToken>
original description, the posterior half of tergum 2 is red in addition to terga 3-4.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="151">
The application of the name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Geoffroy" authorityYear="1785" class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Tenthredo" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tenthredo bimaculata" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bimaculata">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Tenthredo bimaculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to this particular 
<taxonomicName authority="Panzer, 1801" authorityName="Panzer" authorityYear="1801" class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Dolerus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Dolerus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Dolerus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species remains uncertain until the type material (syntype(s) in coll. E. L. Geoffroy, MNHN or Museum 
<normalizedToken originalValue="d’Historié">d'Historie</normalizedToken>
Naturelle 
<normalizedToken originalValue="d’Autun">d'Autun</normalizedToken>
, France?) should be located, or a neotype designated. The diagnosis by 
<bibRefCitation author="Geoffroy, EL" journalOrPublisher="Kongliga Vetenskaps Academiens nya Handlingar" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" refId="B52" refString="Geoffroy, EL, 1785. In: Fourcroy AF de, Entomologia Parisiensis, sive catalogus Insectorum quae in agro parisiensi reperiuntus. Via et Aedibus Serpentineis, Parisiis, [2 volumes] [vii+] 544 pp." title="In: Fourcroy AF de, Entomologia Parisiensis, sive catalogus Insectorum quae in agro parisiensi reperiuntus. Via et Aedibus Serpentineis, Parisiis, [2 volumes] [vii +] 544 pp." year="1785">Geoffroy (1785)</bibRefCitation>
for 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Geoffroy" authorityYear="1785" class="Insecta" family="Tenthredinidae" genus="Tenthredo" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Tenthredo bimaculata" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bimaculata">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">Tenthredo bimaculata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is uninformative: &quot;deux taches blanches au corcelet&quot;, but based on the description by 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.154767" author="Geoffroy, EL" journalOrPublisher="Kongliga Vetenskaps Academiens nya Handlingar" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" refId="B51" refString="Geoffroy, EL, 1762. Histoire abregee des Insectes qui se trouvent aux environs de Paris; Dans laquelle ces Animaux sont ranges suivant un ordre methodique. Durand, Paris, 2: 690 pp. [+plates 11-22.] https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.154767" title="Histoire abregee des Insectes qui se trouvent aux environs de Paris; Dans laquelle ces Animaux sont ranges suivant un ordre methodique. Durand, Paris, 2: 690 pp. [+ plates 11 - 22.]" url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.154767" year="1762">Geoffroy (1762)</bibRefCitation>
it was regarded as a possible senior synonym of 
<taxonomicName family="Tenthredinidae" genus="D." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="D. tristis" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" rank="species" species="tristis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="151">D. tristis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(F.) by 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.10348" author="de Dalla Torre, CG" journalOrPublisher="Berling, Lund" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" refId="B37" refString="de Dalla Torre, CG, 1894. Catalogus Hymenopterorum hucusque descriptorum systematicus et synonymicus. Vol. 1: Tenthredinidae incl. Uroceridae (Phyllophaga &amp; Xylophaga). Guilelmus Engelmann, Lipsiae, [[6] pp.+ pp. I-VIII +] 1-459. https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.10348" title="Catalogus Hymenopterorum hucusque descriptorum systematicus et synonymicus. Vol. 1: Tenthredinidae incl. Uroceridae (Phyllophaga &amp; Xylophaga). Guilelmus Engelmann, Lipsiae, [[ 6] pp. + pp. I-VIII +] 1 - 459." url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.title.10348" year="1894">de Dalla Torre (1894)</bibRefCitation>
. 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.12830" author="Konow, FW" journalOrPublisher="Wiener entomologische Zeitung" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" pagination="1 - 18" refId="B94" refString="Konow, FW, 1897a. Synonymische Bemerkungen zu bisher nicht oder unrichtig gedeuteten Tenthredo Arten bei Geoffroy, Fabricius, Schrank und Villers. Wiener entomologische Zeitung 16: 1 - 18, DOI: https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.12830" title="Synonymische Bemerkungen zu bisher nicht oder unrichtig gedeuteten Tenthredo Arten bei Geoffroy, Fabricius, Schrank und Villers." url="https://doi.org/10.5962/bhl.part.12830" volume="16" year="1897 a">Konow (1897a</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Konow, FW" journalOrPublisher="Genera Insectorum" pageId="0" pageNumber="151" pagination="1 - 176" refId="B99" refString="Konow, FW, 1905b. Hymenoptera. Fam. Tenthredinidae. Genera Insectorum 29: 1 - 176" title="Hymenoptera. Fam. Tenthredinidae." volume="29" year="1905 b">1905b</bibRefCitation>
) subsequently affirmed this synonymy.
</paragraph>
